long.ar,bg,ca,cs,da,de,el,es,es_419,et,fa,fi,:
A Instagram bot which can like some one's recent posts automatically.

Likes are a cost-effective strategy to attract potential followers, which is particularly beneficial for new users.

LikeBot is a extension designed to simplify how you engage with content on Instagram. It allows you to support and interact with other users more efficiently, all without the need for complex setup or compromising your account's safety.

#HOW TO GET STARTED?
1. Select task target type.
2. Enter relevant content and set relevant options.
3. Click the task execution button.

#Features
✅Automatically like posts of each user specified in the custom users list
✅Automatically like posts of the specified user
✅Automatically like posts of each follower of the specified user
✅Automatically like posts of each following of the specified user
✅Automatically like posts of each commenter of the specified post
✅Automatically like posts of each liker of the specified post
✅automatically like posts of the specified hashtag
✅Automatically like posts of the specified location

# FAQ
https://pingapps.top/product-detail?app=IGAutoLike#faq
If you have any problems, don't hesitate to contact us at pingappsteam@tailang.top

# Data Privacy
All the data you process is on your local computer and never passes through our servers.

# Statement
The extension is designed to reduce repetitive work, you shouldn't and can't send a lot of spam, in which case Instagram will ban your account soon.
